When you have three weeks left on your thesis, recoverability is everything.

---

*If you're on macOS and want a no-config LaTeX editor with built-in error parsing, I use TeX64: [https://tex64.com](https://tex64.com). It's what I switched to mid-thesis. Not a sponsored mention — it just happened to be the one that worked for me.*

